whether to resuscitate or not.

29
00:02:59,184 --> 00:03:01,914
And they're not good at decisions.

30
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,644
So how was it with Miss Salander?

31
00:03:03,855 --> 00:03:06,824
She said yes. Do you think
I might be able to see him?

32
00:03:07,058 --> 00:03:09,925
He was asleep the last time I looked,
but let me check.

33
00:03:10,128 --> 00:03:11,618
- Thank you.
- Don't check.

34
00:03:12,063 --> 00:03:14,054
Tell him to pack his things
and leave.

35
00:03:14,266 --> 00:03:16,632
- Mother, please.
- Don't use that tone with me.

36
00:03:16,835 --> 00:03:19,429
