written by a libelist...

43
00:03:40,158 --> 00:03:41,853
...we know who to call.

44
00:03:47,732 --> 00:03:50,132
All right. Thanks.

45
00:03:50,735 --> 00:03:52,828
This way, miss.

46
00:03:56,675 --> 00:03:58,973
<i>If a woman approaches any beast...</i>

47
00:03:59,177 --> 00:04:02,635
<i>... and lies with it, you shall kill</i>
<i>the woman and the beast.</i>

48
00:04:02,847 --> 00:04:04,974
<i>Their blood shall be upon them.</i>

49
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:20,395
<i>My family's impossible.</i>

50
00:04:20,598 --> 00:04:22,691
