62
00:04:56,668 --> 00:04:57,930
I'll keep my mother away.

63
00:04:58,269 --> 00:05:00,396
But please, hurry.

64
00:05:00,905 --> 00:05:01,997
Of course.

65
00:05:14,753 --> 00:05:16,186
Lisbeth.

66
00:05:16,388 --> 00:05:18,083
- I'll get that.
- It's okay.

67
00:05:18,890 --> 00:05:20,289
- Martin Vanger.
- How do you do?

68
00:05:20,492 --> 00:05:21,686
Fine.

69
