93
00:06:33,198 --> 00:06:37,134
- I usually like to smoke outside.
- Sara Witt, 1964.

94
00:06:37,335 --> 00:06:39,235
Daughter of a pastor.
Tied to her bed.

95
00:06:39,437 --> 00:06:42,031
Raped. Charred in the fire
that burned down her house.

96
00:06:42,273 --> 00:06:43,672
Leviticus 21:9.

97
00:06:43,875 --> 00:06:47,106
"The daughter of a priest who profanes
herself by playing the harlot...

98
00:06:47,312 --> 00:06:49,746
...profanes her father
and shall be burned with fire."

99
00:06:49,948 --> 00:06:51,609
Magda Lovisa Sjöberg, 1960.

100
00:06:51,816 --> 00:06:54,182
Found in a barn.
Stabbed and raped with farm tools.

101
00:06:54,385 --> 00:06:56,444
The cow in the next stall
had its throat slit.

102
00:06:56,654 --> 00:06:58,679
Its blood was splashed on her
and hers on it.

103
00:06:58,890 --> 00:07:01,381
Leviticus 20:16.
"If a woman lies with any beast...

104
00:07:01,593 --> 00:07:04,926
...you shall kill the woman and the
beast. Their blood is upon them."

105
00:07:05,130 --> 00:07:06,290
Lea Persson, 1962.

106
00:07:06,498 --> 00:07:09,399
Found by her sister in their pet shop.
Raped, beaten.

107
00:07:09,601 --> 00:07:12,195
The killer uncaged the animals,
smashed the aquariums.

108
00:07:12,403 --> 00:07:14,200
There was a parakeet inside her.

109
00:07:14,739 --> 00:07:16,900
Next, Eva Gustavsson, 1960.

110
00:07:17,108 --> 00:07:21,340
A runaway. Raped, strangled.
A burnt pigeon tied around her neck.

111
00:07:21,813 --> 00:07:25,681
Lena Andersson, 1967. A student.
Raped, stabbed, decapitated...

112
00:07:25,884 --> 00:07:28,182
- Okay.
- I'm not finished.

113
00:07:28,386 --> 00:07:30,217
We're looking for
a serial murderer...

114
00:07:30,421 --> 00:07:33,720
...but what could that have to do
with a teenager living on an island?

115
00:07:34,559 --> 00:07:36,720
She was looking for him too.

116
00:07:37,829 --> 00:07:39,160
<i>Rape. Torture. Fire.</i>

117
00:07:39,364 --> 00:07:41,264
Animals. Religion.

118
00:07:41,633 --> 00:07:43,692
- Am I missing anything?
- The names.

119
00:07:45,103 --> 00:07:46,229
They're all Biblical.

120
00:07:46,437 --> 00:07:48,871
The first woman, the whore,
the Virgin Mary.

121
00:07:49,073 --> 00:07:52,770
Rebecka, Sara,
all from the Old Testament.

122
00:07:52,977 --> 00:07:55,002
Which means they're all Jewish.

123
00:07:56,881 --> 00:08:01,181
One thing the Vangers have more than
their fair share of, it's anti-Semites.

124
00:08:03,855 --> 00:08:06,585
There's one right there.

125
00:08:09,427 --> 00:08:11,486
I can sleep on a couch.

126
00:08:12,330 --> 00:08:13,957
Okay.

127
00:08:14,732 --> 00:08:15,721
Right.

128
00:08:16,534 --> 00:08:20,231
Oh, yeah, there might be
a cat somewhere.

129
00:08:20,438 --> 00:08:21,837
- Good night.
- Night.

130
00:08:22,073 --> 00:08:24,303
Harriet's name isn't.

131
00:08:25,977 --> 00:08:27,069
Isn't what?

132
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:31,048
- Jewish.
- No.

133
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:00,941
- What are you doing?
- Reading your notes.

134
00:09:01,145 --> 00:09:02,612
They're encrypted.

135
00:09:02,814 --> 00:09:05,612
Please. Have some coffee.

136
00:09:05,817 --> 00:09:06,806
Okay.

137
00:09:08,019 --> 00:09:10,385
Then we're gonna have
a very serious conversation...

138
00:09:10,588 --> 00:09:12,818
...about what's yours
and what's mine.

139
00:09:13,758 --> 00:09:16,352
It's amazing what you figured out
with the parade photos.

140
00:09:16,561 --> 00:09:18,188
Thank you.

141
00:09:18,863 --> 00:09:22,196
- It's too bad you don't have hers.
- Whose?

142
00:09:23,534 --> 00:09:24,967
Her.

143
00:09:28,539 --> 00:09:30,268
Can l...? Sorry.

144
00:09:31,676 --> 00:09:32,836
Yeah, all right.

145
00:09:33,044 --> 00:09:34,443
Close that.

146
00:09:34,646 --> 00:09:35,943
No. Not that.

147
00:09:36,881 --> 00:09:38,906
That's the one. Yep.

148
00:09:39,117 --> 00:09:43,679
