on a construction site, years ago.

165
00:11:37,969 --> 00:11:39,527
But...

166
00:11:41,172 --> 00:11:43,470
...she might still be alive.
His widow.

167
00:11:44,409 --> 00:11:46,570
Do you know where
I might find her?

168
00:11:54,619 --> 00:11:56,519
<i>Please drive to highlighted route.</i>

169
00:11:57,555 --> 00:12:02,015
In 1966, you were in Hedestad
with your husband.

170
00:12:03,728 --> 00:12:05,161
