171
00:12:05,363 --> 00:12:06,557
A local photographer.

172
00:12:06,764 --> 00:12:08,595
You were taking pictures
too that day...

173
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:11,894
...and I'd love to look at them
if by some miracle you have them.

174
00:12:12,103 --> 00:12:14,401
It wouldn't be a miracle.
We were on our honeymoon.

175
00:12:14,739 --> 00:12:16,468
But why?

176
00:12:16,674 --> 00:12:20,735
This girl here. Here, you can see
her better in the enlargement.

177
00:12:20,945 --> 00:12:23,379
See, that's you there.
Just after this was taken...

178
00:12:23,581 --> 00:12:26,982
...after she'd seen something
across the street, she was murdered.

179
00:12:28,953 --> 00:12:31,046
How awful.

180
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:43,492
- There you are.
- Thank you.

181
00:13:02,553 --> 00:13:04,350
Would you mind if I made
a copy of this?

182
00:13:04,555 --> 00:13:05,544
