you can bribe...

194
00:14:16,327 --> 00:14:20,093
...to swear under oath he can find
absolutely nothing wrong with me.

195
00:14:20,331 --> 00:14:22,458
And stop visiting
tattoo-removal websites.

196
00:14:22,867 --> 00:14:24,266
Or I'll do it again...

197
00:14:25,836 --> 00:14:27,360
...right here.

198
00:17:15,673 --> 00:17:18,141
- Is that dental floss?
- Yes.

199
00:17:21,679 --> 00:17:23,670
You're gonna sterilize that, right?

200
00:17:27,518 --> 00:17:29,611
Couldn't we just use tape
or something?

201
00:17:29,820 --> 00:17:31,185
No.

202
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:33,579
What?

203
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:38,860
Thank you. Jesus!

204
00:17:39,063 --> 00:17:41,691
- Drink.
- Okay.

205
