- Don't move.
- You're not a doctor.

207
00:18:02,486 --> 00:18:04,977
- Take off your wet clothes.
- What?

208
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:08,350
Yeah. Thank you.

209
00:18:10,427 --> 00:18:13,396
Yeah, I think it has stopped bleeding.

210
