This is fucking madness.

213
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:38,350
You're okay, you're okay,
you're okay.

214
00:18:42,193 --> 00:18:44,855
Jesus, that hurts. Fuck.

215
00:18:50,935 --> 00:18:54,530
This is insane.
I mean, these people...

216
00:18:54,939 --> 00:18:58,102
Somebody was shooting at me.
I mean, it wasn't an accident.

217
00:18:58,342 --> 00:19:00,276
No one's shooting at you now.

218
00:19:03,714 --> 00:19:05,739
You know, I'm pretty sure
this is a bad idea.

219
00:19:05,950 --> 00:19:07,008
