226
00:20:30,701 --> 00:20:33,670
- I like working with you.
- I like working with you too.

227
00:20:41,011 --> 00:20:43,445
- It could have been a stray shot.
- Not by Gunnar.

228
00:20:43,647 --> 00:20:45,740
